# propertyList

**Instance Property**

An object that contains data to associate with the command.

## Declaration

```swift
@MainActor var propertyList: Any? { get }
```

## Discussion

Use [doc://com.apple.uikit/documentation/UIKit/UICommand/propertyList] to associate a small amount of data to the command.



## Associating data

- **UICommandTagShare**: A value that identifies a command as a Share menu.
